{"tid":957790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣西18億新醫院落成 網民：似馬桶","createTime":"2018-12-27T09:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T08:18:34.000Z","uid":150685,"like":291,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"3bf0ee4c4f1d472ae392fdf3b57e14873ea41b86","tid":957790,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181226/large/1545812411_7efb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181226%2Flarge%2F1545812411_7efb.jpg&h=33102c46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒報道，一幢在廣西落成僅約2個月的新醫院，近日吸引不少人的「目光」。<br />\n據悉，這間名為「廣西國際壯醫醫院」是一座非牟利的公立綜合性民族醫醫院，位於南寧市五象新區，佔地300畝，建築總面積18.75萬平方米，總投資達15.56億元人民幣（約18億港元）。該醫院今年10月23日正式開業，不過不少看過航拍影片的網民都批評，新醫院外形似馬桶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181226/59071924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181226%2F59071924&d=idkdSC%2BxPlwqqHT1giX9Gi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=b29d94e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181226%2F59071924&h=9fb999b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181226/59071924</a><br />\n<br />\n香港都有個千億西九山墳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e198ee2e433d907cc4bda55c907fcd27a539d56","tid":957790,"uid":10757,"like":279,"dislike":2,"score":277,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:55:48.000Z","msg":"18億港元<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我地起條橋就冇"},{"pid":"dabe0a792001a2abaac2b89842a59c08e68c8728","tid":957790,"uid":22481,"like":268,"dislike":0,"score":268,"quote":{"pid":"7e198ee2e433d907cc4bda55c907fcd27a539d56","tid":957790,"uid":10757,"like":279,"dislike":2,"score":277,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:55:48.000Z","msg":"18億港元<img src=\"/ass