0cb12ac2f79","tid":957790,"uid":42364,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:20:22.000Z","msg":"之前大埔有個避雨亭630萬姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夠起二三百個"},{"pid":"f3121ee78791d99e0b63f73259c6d6839228de6b","tid":957790,"uid":202698,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:25:44.000Z","msg":"拎香港天水圍醫院比較一下<br />\n<br />\n【本網訊】為應付新界西醫療聯網內的醫療需求，署理食物及衛生局局長陳肇始昨於立法會衛生事務委員會會議中宣布，<span style=\"color: red;\">計劃耗資約39億興建天水圍醫院。</span>當局期望可於明年第1季向財委會爭取撥款，至2016年第2季完成有關工程。<br />\n<br />\n天水圍醫院的建築工程於2013年第一季開展，並在2016年9月竣工，樓面<span style=\"color: red;\">面積約為59,000平方米，預計日後可提供300張病床。</span>天水圍醫院外圍設有玻璃幕牆，設計可加強採納天然光；而醫院在部份樓層綠化花園，既增加環保元素，也可美化景觀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天水圍醫院：5萬9000平方米，39億港元<br />\n廣西醫院：18.75萬平方米，18億港元<br />\n<br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0761cef01915d50ce18b44a23412a954dd07d23c","tid":957790,"uid":53705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a4160dc5c7011f0f47379e7f4f2ed12e9f89ef2f","tid":957790,"uid":57659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b314810384126496edb50fe4555c7a72ae4ed63d","tid":957790,"uid":108467,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"7e198ee2e433d907cc4bda55c907fcd27a539d56","tid":957790,"uid":10757,"like":279,"dislike":2,"score":277,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:55:48.000Z","msg":"18億港元<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我地起條橋就冇"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:16:03.000Z","msg":"可能偷工減料得好西利🤔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:40:23.000Z","msg":"18億係講啫<br />\n事實用咗唔知有冇1/3<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T13:28:09.000Z","msg":"如果係咁, 即係證明 廣西仲勁<br />\n<br />\n用6億就起到間醫院 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asse